title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Element Mini
description:
A smaller version of our best selling Element, making it a rocker designed for kids who want to ride it all. The Element Mini delivers performance on mountain, in the park, and well beyond; the quintessential do everything design for Jr.
